60.4	Zhang_Ziyi	Zhang Ziyi	Zhang Ziyi (born 9 February 1979) is a Chinese film actress coined by the media as one of the Four Young Dan actresses (四小花旦) in the Film Industry in China, along with Zhao Wei, Xu Jinglei, and Zhou Xun. With a string of Chinese and international hits to her name, she has worked with renowned directors such as Zhang Yimou, Ang Lee, Wong Kar-wai, Chen Kaige, Tsui Hark, Lou Ye, Seijun Suzuki, Feng Xiaogang and Rob Marshall.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d1/ZhangZiyi_Amfar.jpg/220px-ZhangZiyi_Amfar.jpg
